title: Angle between Möbius spheres

The hyperspheres corresponding to two points $$[s_1],[s_2]$$ outside $$S^2$$ intersect at an angle $$\theta$$ determined by

$$
\cos\theta=
\frac
{\langle s_1,s_2\rangle}
{\sqrt{\langle s_1,s_1\rangle\langle s_2,s_2\rangle}}.
$$

This angle is determined up to $$\theta\leftrightarrow\pi-\theta.$$